<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="through-prep">through <strong><em>prep</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /θruː/    美 /θruː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>穿过；通过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They drove through a snowstorm. 
他们驱车穿过暴风雪。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Light comes in through the window. 
光线透过窗户射进来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I couldn’t hear their conversation through the wall.
我隔着墙听不到他们的谈话。</p></div>

<h3 id="across-through">辨析 across , through</h3>
<p>二者都有“穿过”的意思。<br />
<strong>across</strong>  指横过，表示动作从一边到另一边沿物体的表面进行。
**through ** 指从中间穿过，表示动作在某立体空间中进行。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It took us hours to walk through the forest.
我们费了几个小时才穿过森林。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>从头到尾：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The children were too young to sit through a concert.
这些孩子太小，音乐会没结束就坐不住了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>遍及；在...中间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>tour through France 
周游法国</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a walk through the flowers 
在花丛中散步</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>(做) 完...；(耗) 尽...：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>get through a book 
看完一本书</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>经由；以：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>From then on, we’ve kept in touch with each other through e-mails. 
从那时起，我们通过电子邮件保持联系。</p><footer>2010 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Graduation is a good time to thank those who have helped you <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the tough years.  （2011 上海）<br />
A.through<br />
B.up<br />
C.with<br />
D.from  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  </p></div>